-------------------------------------------
Combo Release V00-00-00

June 12, 2018 Kevin Meagher
---------------------------
V00-04-02

- Add documentation for `TrackHitsDistributionSmoothness` and `TrackHitsSeparationLength`
- Use `direct_hits.get_default_definitions()` function rather than global variable
- Script Cleanup (remove `Finish()` and `TrashCan`

March 24, 2017 Anna Pollmann (anna.pollmann@uni-wuppertal.de)
------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-04-01

- Switch all projects to using our own serialization library
- python3 fixup
- added StdDevDomDistQTotDom variable
	-- Alex Burgman


March 24, 2017 Anna Pollmann (anna.pollmann@uni-wuppertal.de)
------------------------------------------------------------------
Release	V00-04-00

- added the TimeCharacteristics Module incl. a bunch of new tested variables
	-- Anna Pollmann
- class definition and converters moved to recclasses


